name: Bonding - D2O
desc: Tribute 2 "Deuterion" and 1 "Oxygeddon" from your hand and/or field; Special Summon 1 "Water Dragon" or "Water Dragon Cluster" from your hand, Deck, or GY. (This Special Summon is treated as a Special Summon with "Bonding - H2O".) If "Water Dragon" or "Water Dragon Cluster" is sent from the field to your GY while this card is in your GY: Add this card to your hand. You can only use this effect of "Bonding - D2O" once per turn.
